OL,3,CChildcare sector under 'significant
OL,4,Cstress' as most struggle to get staff
OL,6,FLess than half of two-year-olds in
OL,7,FGuernsey are attending a nursery or
OL,8,Fpre-school, according to an
OL,9,Findependent report into the state of
OL,10,Fearly years education.
OL,12,FThe review, carried out by Island
OL,13,FGlobal Research, shows that challenges
OL,14,Fincluding poor staff retention, low
OL,15,Fwages and struggles to recruit
OL,16,Foverseas staff have led to limitations
OL,17,Fon child spaces.
