OL,3,CChildcare sector under 'significant
OL,4,Cstress' as most struggle to get staff
OL,6,FIn the survey, which canvased 24 out
OL,7,Fof 30 Guernsey pre-schools and
OL,8,Fnurseries, 95% said they struggle to
OL,9,Frecruit staff on-island, with 71%
OL,10,Fadding they have problems with
OL,11,Frecruitment and retention.
OL,13,FNearly half of the providers also said
OL,14,Fthey find recruiting staff from
OL,15,Foutside Guernsey difficult.
OL,17,FOne of those pre-schools, Little Rays
OL,18,Fof Sunshine, normally has places for
OL,19,F90 children but is capping numbers at
OL,20,F70 as it struggles to find enough
OL,21,Fstaff to meet legal requirements.
