OL,3,CChildcare sector under 'significant
OL,4,Cstress' as most struggle to get staff
OL,6,FManager Sian Butt told ITV News:
OL,7,F"We've got really fine margins. We
OL,8,Fhave to hire more staff than we need
OL,9,Fbecause we need to cover staff
OL,10,Fsickness, staff holidays. We can't
OL,11,Foffer big wages so a lot of people
OL,12,Fleave the industry.
OL,14,F"When we're trying to recruit from
OL,15,Foverseas, we don't come under any of
OL,16,Fthe policy for licences so we have to
OL,17,Fapply out of policy, which can then be
OL,18,Frejected and they're quite costly."
