OL,3,CChildcare sector under 'significant
OL,4,Cstress' as most struggle to get staff
OL,6,FParents are concerned about waiting
OL,7,Flists too, given the current shortfall
OL,8,Fin places offered by early years
OL,9,Fproviders.
OL,11,FOne said: "A lot of the conversations
OL,12,Fyou have at baby groups and with mums
OL,13,Fis about how early you've got to get
OL,14,Fon a waiting list to get your babies
OL,15,Finto nurseries because the demand is
OL,16,Fquite high to get them in at that
OL,17,Fyounger age and to get back into work."
