OL,3,CChildcare sector under 'significant
OL,4,Cstress' as most struggle to get staff
OL,6,FThe politician who called for the
OL,7,Freview into early years provision,
OL,8,FDeputy Sasha Kazantseva-Miller, wants
OL,9,Fto see the States take issues faced by
OL,10,Fthe sector more seriously.
OL,12,FShe said: "It's very clear that
OL,13,Fthey're under significant stress. I
OL,14,Fthink it's really important that with
OL,15,Fplummeting birth rates, the cost of
OL,16,Fchildcare and cost of living in
OL,17,Fgeneral, we really look, as part of
OL,18,Fthe next tax debate, at supporting the
OL,19,Fprovision of childcare because I think
OL,20,Fit really affects our economy."
