OL,6,FAn early years provider in Jersey told
OL,7,FITV News that they too struggle to
OL,8,Frecruit off-island staff due to the
OL,9,Fadditional costs it adds, including
OL,10,Fwork licences, and issues are also
OL,11,Fbeing faced in the UK.
